text: The Hunters () is a 1996 Swedish thriller movie directed by Kjell Sundvall and starring Rolf Lassgård, Lennart Jähkel, Jarmo Mäkinen, Tomas Norström, Göran Forsmark, and Rolf Degerlund. The sequel was followed in 2011. ==Other websites== * * Category:1996 thriller movies Category:Swedish thriller movies Category:Movies directed by Kjell Sundvall
